<:p>- Belmont, the home of Portia in "The Merchant of Venice". Its present-day location has been much debated.</:p>
<:p>- Birnam Wood appears in: "Macbeth shall never vanquished be until // Great Birnam wood to high Dunsinane hill // Shall come against him." "Macbeth", 4.1.</:p>
